    "content": "[Intro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-2~----5~-7~-|\r\nE|----5~-------| (X2)[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Ooh, I can't go any further than this\r\nG|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-2~----5~-7~-|\r\nE|----5~-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Ooh, I want you so badly, it's my biggest wish\r\nG|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-2~----5~-7~-|\r\nE|----5~-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\n\r\n[tab]I spent my time just thinkin thinkin thinkin bout you\r\nEvery single day yes, I'm really missin' missin' you\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]And all those things we use to use to use to do\r\nHey girl, wuz up, it use to be just me and you\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]I spent my time just thinkin thinkin thinkin bout you\r\nEvery single day, yes I'm really missin missin you\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]And all those things we use to use to use to do\r\nHey girl wuz up, wuz up, wuz up, wuz up\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]Can you meet me halfway? Right at the boarderline\r\nThat's where i'm gonna wait, for you\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]I'll be lookin out, night and day\r\nTook my heart to the limit, and this is where I'll stay\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]I can't go any further than this\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]I want you so bad it's my only wish\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\n\r\n[tab]Girl, I travel 'round the world and even sail the seven seas\r\nAcross the universe I go to other galaxies\r\nG|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-7-|\r\nE|-----------------5-5-5-5-5-5-5-5---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Just 